    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. It\u2019s been kept in absolute pristine condition\u2014seriously, it still has that new car smell and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been my pride and joy, always garaged and meticulously cared for. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a new adventure, this is the one. Come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
