    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the legendary S54 platform, featuring a high-revving 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS. The powertrain is mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, delivering linear torque to the rear wheels via a factory M-variable differential lock. This specimen boasts a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive service history addressing all critical preventative maintenance. The chassis remains taut with original suspension geometry, and the ventilated braking system provides exceptional thermal management. Finished in a flawless factory coat with an interior devoid of bolster wear, this is a turnkey investment for the discerning purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
