      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, shielded from the elements since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections, further protected by a premium ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the leather seats show zero bolster wear, the carpets are pristine, and the original 'new car' scent remains. Every button, switch, and electronic feature functions perfectly. Mechanically, it is flawless, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified technicians using OEM parts. This is a rare opportunity to own a non-smoker, single-owner example that has been pampered with an open checkbook policy. If you are looking for the finest specimen available on the market, your search ends here.",
